<view class="container">
  <view class="card">
    <view class="title">学习记录管理</view>
    <view class="muted">
      这里可以按全部科目、指定科目或指定章节清理练习进度与记录。所有操作都会二次确认。
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="sub-title">清理范围</view>

    <picker mode="selector" range="{{subjectNames}}" value="{{subjectIndex}}" bindchange="onSubjectChange">
      <view class="picker-row">
        <view>科目</view>
        <view class="picker-value">{{currentSubjectName}} ▼</view>
      </view>
    </picker>

    <picker
      wx:if="{{currentSubjectId !== 'all'}}"
      mode="selector"
      range="{{chapterNames}}"
      value="{{chapterIndex}}"
      bindchange="onChapterChange"
    >
      <view class="picker-row">
        <view>章节</view>
        <view class="picker-value">{{currentChapterName}} ▼</view>
      </view>
    </picker>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="sub-title">清空练习进度</view>
    <view class="muted block-desc">
      清空练习进度只会重置对应练习中的“已做状态”和进度条，不会删除错题、收藏、备注和题库。
    </view>

    <button class="manage-btn blue-btn" bindtap="clearSequenceProgress">
      清空顺序练习进度
    </button>

    <button class="manage-btn orange-btn" bindtap="clearWrongPracticeProgress">
      清空错题练习进度
    </button>

    <button class="manage-btn purple-btn" bindtap="clearFavoritePracticeProgress">
      清空收藏夹练习进度
    </button>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="sub-title">清空记录</view>
    <view class="muted block-desc">
      清空错题记录会让题目移出错题集；清空收藏记录会让题目移出收藏夹。备注、顺序练习进度和题库不会被删除。
    </view>

    <button class="manage-btn light-red-btn" bindtap="clearWrongRecords">
      清空错题记录
    </button>

    <button class="manage-btn light-red-btn" bindtap="clearFavoriteRecords">
      清空收藏记录
    </button>
  </view>
</view>